outputs.output_descr: This project will support the national government and local governments in order to formulate a strategic framework for early recovery. This process will be led by the ministry of Planning and the ministry of civil Protection (COPECO). This early recovery framework will include prioritized sectors (by the government) as temporary shelter, housing and livelihoods
